parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or jerk while shifting gears, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or jerks while shifting gears
the transmission slips or fails to engage
the overdrive light blinks
the vehicle loses power
and the transmission makes grinding or knocking noises.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch and gear shifting system can cause the vehicle to hesitate or jerk while shifting gears, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear axle and differential can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or jerk while driving, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The vehicle makes grinding or knocking noises

the vehicle vibrates or shakes while driving
the vehicle loses power or hesitates while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the throttle body and engine can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or jerk while driving, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.

the vehicle loses power or hesitates while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear liftgate hinge can cause the glass to fall out of position, potentially causing injury or damage to the vehicle or surrounding objects.
symptoms: The hinge breaks
the glass falls out of position

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracked rear panel can allow water to seep in, causing rust and corrosion, and potentially leading to safety issues.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The fuel system issues can cause the vehicle to stall or fail to start, leading to safety risks.

fuel system too lean.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission and timing chain issues can cause the vehicle to stall or fail to start, leading to safety risks.
